# Bipartite Chart - KX Dashboards

Original URL: https://code.kx.com/dashboards/bipartite/

# Bipartite Chart

![Screenshot](../img/bipartite/bipartewhite.jpg)

A unique two-way interactive chart featuring two independent data sets and
associated relationships. Compatible with Pivot/OLAP data.

## Basics

![Screenshot](../img/bipartite/bipartitebasics.png)

_Name_

    A name for the component provided by the user. 
_Data Source_

     [Data sources](../datasources/)
_Focus_

    A [View State Parameter](../viewstateparameters/) for [linking](../viewstateparameters/#linking-components) components

### Actions

[Actions](../action/)

## LHS Data

![Screenshot](../img/bipartite/lefthandcomparemenu.jpg)

_Series Key_

    A _Data Source_ column: the independent variable to categorize right-hand dependent variables

## RHS Data

### Data

![Screenshot](../img/bipartite/righthandcomparemenu.jpg)

_Series Data_

    A _Data Source_ column to include in the right-hand data set
_Display Name_

    For _Column_

## Labels

![Screenshot](../img/bipartite/bipartitelabels.jpg)

_Show_

    Display Bipartite labels
_Position_

    Adjust label position in pixels
_Format_

    Define format of Data labels. Select from `General`, `Number`, `Smart Number`, `Formatted Number`, `Datetime`
_Decimal Places_

    Define number of decimal places for number formats
_Hide Trailing Zeroes_

    Remove excess zeroes at the end of the number
_Date/Time format_

    For `Datetime` format
_Width_

    Pixel width between chart and chart value (occupied by the label)

## Values

![Screenshot](../img/bipartite/bipartitevalues.jpg)

_Show_

    Display Bipartite values
_Position_

    Adjust position of values in pixels
_Format_

    Define format of Data labels. Select from `General`, `Number`, `Smart Number`, `Formatted Number`, `Datetime`
_Decimal Places_

    Define number of decimal places for number formats
_Width_

    Pixel width between value and label.

## Percentages

![Screenshot](../img/bipartite/bipartitepercentages.jpg)

_Show_

    Display relative data distribution percentages
_Position_

    Adjust position of percentage values in pixels
_Width_

    Pixel width between percentage label and value label.

## Padding

![Screenshot](../img/bipartite/bipartitepadding.jpg)

_Left_

_Right_

_Top_

_Bottom_

    Set padding of bipartite chart within the component

